    <span class="h1 enlighten">Help if you use <b>Fuel Direct</b>
    </span>
  </h1>
  <div slot="paragraph">
    <p>If you pay for your energy directly out of your benefits payments. This is sometimes called ‘third party deductions’.</p>
    <p>British Gas aim to reassess Fuel Direct plans at least twice a year. We will contact the Department for Work and Pensions (DWP) if your payments need to change, and the DWP will notify you.</p>
  </div>
