      <h3 slot="heading">Further information</h3>

      <ns-expander role="tab">
        <h4 slot="heading">Help if you're struggling to pay for your energy</h4>
        <p>We know it's not always easy to pay your bill – and that everyone's circumstances are different.
        <p>Last year, we helped over 300,000 customers manage their debt, and we're here for you too.</p>
        <p>We now have a dedicated page to help our customers <a href="https://www.britishgas.co.uk/help-and-support/bills-and-payments/help-if-youre-struggling-to-pay">take control of their energy debt</a> – including any financial hardships caused by Covid-19.</p>
      </ns-expander>

      <ns-expander role="tab">
        <h4 slot="heading">Free advice if you’re struggling financially</h4>
        <p>If you struggling to pay your bills, you can get free independent advice from a number of organisations.</p>
        <h3>Need debt or money advice?</h3>
        <p>Income Max offers free independent money advice to help you stay on top of your finances. <a class="external-link-icon" aria-label="Opens in new window" href="http://www.incomemax.co.uk/" target="_blank">Visit the Income Max website</a>.</p>

        <p>And if you're looking for free debt advice, <a class="external-link-icon" aria-label="Opens in new window" href="https://www.tully.co.uk/british-gas" target="_blank">visit the Tully website</a>. There you can build a budget online in minutes and get independent support to get you back on track.</p>

        <h3>Energy efficiency and fuel poverty</h3>

        <p>Agility Eco offer energy efficiency advice as well as free boilers and white goods for people struggling financially. <a class="external-link-icon" aria-label="Opens in new window" href="https://www.agilityeco.co.uk/our-solutions/" target="_blank">Visit the Agility Eco website</a>.</p>

        <p>Or take a look at our own <a>Struggling to Pay page</a> to find out how we can make your energy bills more manageable.</p>
      </ns-expander>

      <ns-expander role="tab">
        <h4 slot="heading">Cancelling your Fuel Direct scheme</h4>
        <p>If you'd like to cancel your Fuel Direct, you'll need to get in touch with the Department for Work and Pensions. They'll let us know and we'll cancel the scheme for you.</p>
      </ns-expander>

      <ns-expander role="tab">
        <h4 slot="heading">Protecting you against scammers</h4>
        <p>We work with National Trading Standards on a programme called <b>Friends Against Scams</b> to keep you and you loved ones safe from scams and fraud. <a class="external-link-icon" aria-label="Opens in new window" href="https://www.friendsagainstscams.org.uk/" target="_blank">Visit the Friends Against Scams website</a>.</p>
      </ns-expander>

      <ns-expander role="tab">
        <h4 slot="heading">Need help with your water bills?</h4>

        <p>Utility bills can stack up. So if you're struggling to pay for your water bill too, you may be eligible for your water supplier's Priority Services Register. Not sure who your supplier is?  <a class="external-link-icon" aria-label="Opens in new window" href="https://www.water.org.uk/advice-for-customers/find-your-supplier/" target="_blank">Use our handy tool</a>.</p>
      </ns-expander>
